BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 328.88 Tm (and that the username exists in the live database before resetting anything.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 315.38 Tm (- If a user forgets the rotated password later, use the normal password reset workflow from the login page.) Tj ET
